###############################################################
# SALMONELLA BLOOD TRANSCRIPTOME SEVERITY ANALYSIS PIPELINE
# ===========================================================
#
# PURPOSE:
# Detect severe vs normal bacterial infection responses
# from mouse blood transcriptome logFC data.
#
# INPUT:
# 3 CSV files containing:
#
# gene,logFC
#
# EXAMPLE:
# IL6,3.5
# S100A8,5.2
#
# FEATURES:
# - Uppercase-safe gene matching
# - Severe infection signature scoring
# - Normal/controlled response scoring
# - Pathway subgrouping
# - Heatmaps
# - Radar plots
# - Severity classification
# - Gene-level categorization
#
###############################################################

############################
# LOAD LIBRARIES
############################

